## Tooling (content)

- `pre-commit run --all-files` — lint everything (markdownlint autofixes via `--fix`).
- `markdownlint .` — lint Markdown · style overrides live in `.markdownlint.jsonc`.
- CI runs a link check (lychee) over all `*.md`; broken links fail the build.
- Docs live in `docs/`; start from `docs/index.md`.
